trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderMapping" /> class represents a SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderMapping" /> 類別表示 SOAP 標頭對應。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value that indicates whether the SOAP header mapping is custom-defined.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> 值，指出 SOAP 標頭對應是否是自訂定義的。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the SOAP header mapping is custom-defined; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 SOAP 標頭對應是自訂定義的，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> value that indicates the direction of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> 值，表示 SOAP 標頭對應的方向。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> value that indicates the direction of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderDirection" /> 值，表示 SOAP 標頭對應的方向。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that represents the type of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Type" />，表示 SOAP 標頭對應的型別。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Type" /> that represents the type of the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Type" />，表示 SOAP 標頭對應的型別。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" /> associated with the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: 取得與 SOAP 標頭對應相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" /> associated with the SOAP header mapping.
trans-unit.target: 與 SOAP 標頭對應相關聯的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.MemberInfo" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> value that indicates whether the SOAP header mapping repeats.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> 值，指出 SOAP 標頭對應是否重複。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the SOAP header mapping repeats; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 SOAP 標頭對應重複，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。
